casebody.data:
No. 455. Celotex Co. et al. v. Masonite Corp. October 16, 1933.

Dismissed per stipulation of counsel.

Messrs. Henry M. Huxley, Caleb S. Layton, and George L. Wilkinson for petitioners. Messrs. Drury W. Cooper, Hugh M. Morris, and Herbert H. Dyke for respondent.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the Circuit Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit.
